    "Id": 7,
    "Content": "\n### Building from Source\n\n#### Prerequisites\n\n- Rust 1.77.2 or later\n- Node.js 18 or later\n- webkit2gtk-4.1 (libwebkit2gtk-4.1 for debian)\n- npm or yarn\n\n#### Steps\n\n1. Clone the repository:\n",
